\c 19
\s Imizi yokuphephela
\p
\v 1 Lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho isiqumile izizwe\x + 12.29.\x*, olizwe lazo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunike lona, osusidla ilifa lazo, osuhlala emizini yazo lezindlini zazo,
\v 2 imizi emithathu uzazehlukanisela yona phakathi kwelizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona ukudla ilifa lalo\x + Eks. 21.13. Nani 35.10,14. Josh. 20.2,8.\x*.
\v 3 Uzazilungisela indlela, wehlukanise umngcele welizwe lakho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona ukudla ilifa lalo, ube lezigaba ezintathu, ukuze wonke umbulali abalekele khona.
\p
\v 4 Lalolu ludaba lombulali ongabalekela khona ukuze aphile: Lowo otshaya umakhelwane wakhe kungeyisikho ngabomo, obengamzondi mandulo\x + 4.42. Nani 35.15.\x*,
\v 5 njengongena egangeni lomakhelwane wakhe ukuyagamula izihlahla, lesandla sakhe sitshaya ngehloka ukugamula isihlahla, lensimbi ikhumuke emphinini, imtshaye umakhelwane wakhe aze afe, yena uzabalekela komunye waleyomizi ukuze aphile.
\v 6 Hlezi umphindiseli wegazi axotshane lombulali, inhliziyo yakhe isatshisa, amfice ngoba indlela inde, amtshaye ambulale, lanxa bekungelasigwebo sokufa kuye, ngoba ebengamzondi mandulo\x + Nani 35.12,19.\x*.
\v 7 Ngalokhu ngiyalilaya ngisithi: Uzazehlukanisela imizi emithathu.
\v 8 Uba-ke iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 12.20.\x* iqhelisa umngcele wakho\x + 12.20.\x*, njengokufunga kwayo kuboyihlo, ikunika ilizwe lonke eyakhuluma ngalo ukubanika oyihlo\x + Gen. 15.18-21.\x*,
\v 9 uba ugcina yonke limithetho ukuyenza engikulaya yona lamuhla, ukuthanda iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, lokuhamba endleleni zayo izinsuku zonke, khona uzazengezelelela eminye imizi emithathu ngaphandle kwaleyo emithathu\x + 19.2. Josh. 20.7.\x*.
\v 10 Ukuze kungachithwa igazi elingelacala phakathi kwelizwe lakho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona ukuba yilifa, ube lecala legazi phezu kwakho.
\p
\v 11 Kodwa uba umuntu elenzondo kumakhelwane wakhe, amcathamele, amvukele, amtshaye okokufa aze afe, abalekele komunye walimizi\x + Nani 35.16-21. Dute. 27.24.\x*,
\v 12 khona abadala bomuzi wakhe bazathumela bamthathe lapho, bamnikele esandleni somphindiseli wegazi ukuthi afe.
\v 13 Ilihlo lakho lingamhawukeli\x + 19.21. Dute. 7.16.\x*, kodwa uzakhupha igazi elingelacala koIsrayeli, ukuze kukulungele\x + 19.10. Nani 35.33. Dute. 21.9. 1 Kho. 2.31.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Ungatshedisi isikhonkwane somngcele womakhelwane wakho abendulo abasibethelayo elifeni lakho, ozakudla ilifa lalo elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona ukudla ilifa lalo\x + 27.17. Zaga 22.28. 23.10. Hos. 5.10. Jobe 24.2.\x*.
\s Umlayo wobufakazi
\p
\v 15 Umfakazi oyedwa kayikusukumela umuntu loba ngabuphi ububi loba ngasiphi isono, loba kusiphi isono one ngaso. Ngomlomo wabafakazi ababili kumbe ngomlomo wabafakazi abathathu udaba lungaqiniswa\x + Nani 35.30. Mat. 18.16. Joha. 8.17. 2 Kor. 13.1. 1 Tim. 5.19. Heb. 10.28.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Uba kusukuma umfakazi wamanga amelane lomuntu emfakazela ngokubi\x + Hlab. 35.11. Hlab. 27.12. Dute. 19.18.\x*,
\v 17 khona abantu bobabili, abalokuxabana, bazakuma phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, phambi kwabapristi labahluleli abazakuba bekhona ngalezonsuku\x + 17.8,9. Dute. 21.5.\x*.
\v 18 Labahluleli bazachwayisisa; khangela-ke umfakazi ngumfakazi wamanga, ufakaze amanga ngomfowabo\x + 13.14.\x*,
\v 19 khona lizakwenza kuye lokho abehlose ukukwenza kumfowabo\x + Zaga 19.5,9. Dan. 6.24.\x*; ngalokhu uzakhupha ububi phakathi kwakho\x + 13.5.\x*.
\v 20 Lalabo abaseleyo bazakuzwa, besabe, kusukela lapho bangabe besenza ububi obunjengalobu phakathi kwakho\x + 13.11. Dute. 21.21.\x*.
\v 21 Lelihlo lakho lingabi lesihawu\x + 19.13.\x*; impilo ngempilo, ilihlo ngelihlo, izinyo ngezinyo, isandla ngesandla, unyawo ngonyawo\x + Eks. 21.23,24.\x*.
